png?w=3804&amp;ssl=1 3804w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/03/confetti-eased-2-1.png?resize=300%2C156&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/03/confetti-eased-2-1.png?resize=1024%2C533&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/03/confetti-eased-2-1.png?resize=768%2C400&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/03/confetti-eased-2-1.png?resize=1536%2C800&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/03/confetti-eased-2-1.png?resize=2048%2C1067&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2023/03/confetti-eased-2-1.png?w=3000&amp;ssl=1 3000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3804px) 100vw, 3804px\" /><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-content-justification-center is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-8 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2023/05/wp20-logo-white.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"29\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.1\">Join a celebration online or around the globe for the 20th anniversary of WordPress. ↗&#65038;</p>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</a>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"intro\" style=\"padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-container-15 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:120px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:120px;padding-left:0px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-13 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:80%\"><h1 class=\"wp-block-wporg-random-heading has-heading-cta-font-size\">WordPress: Grow your <em>business</em></h1></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:20%\"></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Create a place for your business, your interests, or anything else—with the open source platform that powers the web.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"/download/\">Get WordPress</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-wporg-language-suggest alignfull\"></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"padding-top:5rem;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);min-height:670px\" id=\"editor\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"></span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-11558\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2022/08/Editor.webp\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" /><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-white-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-1b98fadf6cdf2c39fec402247b767054 is-layout-constrained wp-container-17 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-right has-pomegrade-3-color has-text-color has-heading-cta-font-size\">Dream it, build&nbsp;it</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">That’s the beauty of using blocks. See exactly how your site will look in real time, even as you add, edit, and rearrange your content. Create any kind of custom site with intuitive editing, flexible design tools, and powerful features to manage it all.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"/gutenberg/\">Explore the WordPress Editor ↗&#65038;</a></p>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-blueberry-4-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"benefits\" style=\"padding-top:5rem;padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-bottom:5rem;padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-21 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-2-font-size\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:100px;margin-bottom:40px\">Powerful and empowering</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"601\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2022/08/theme-styles.png\" alt=\"An illustration showing a grid of different type styles and color options, with a cursor arrow making a selection.\" class=\"wp-image-11481\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/08/theme-styles.png?w=960&amp;ssl=1 960w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/08/theme-styles.png?resize=300%2C188&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/08/theme-styles.png?resize=768%2C481&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-20 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Style it your way</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Design anything you imagine. Start with a blank canvas or choose from a wide variety of <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/\">themes</a> and <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/patterns/\">patterns</a>. Customize every detail, from color and fonts to layouts and functionality.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Plug in and extend</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Make WordPress do whatever you need it to. Add a store, mailing list, portfolio, social feed, analytics; you’re in control with over 55,000 plugins.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Own what you make&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Your content, your design, and your data always belong to you. With WordPress you’re free to tell your story, grow your brand, or simply be yourself.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\"><strong>Create with confidence</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-short-text\">Built by an open source community with decades of experience, its passionate contributors are committed to keeping WordPress as stable and secure as possible.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-white-color has-charcoal-1-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-76d849fb94a3900449106dfdbb324b68 is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"showcase\" style=\"padding-top:5rem\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--edge-space)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-container-26 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-2-font-size\">One platform, millions of possibilities</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-25 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-fl